; Regression test for issue #687: Budgeting bug? (BZ#687)
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/687
;
; Bug: --add-budget reg produced empty output when only a periodic transaction
; exists and no real transactions match the account. Adding at least one real
; transaction caused the budget entries to appear.

~ Monthly from 2009-08-01
  Cash:NewCar          $-200
  Income:NewCar

test --add-budget reg Cash:NewCar --begin 2009/08/01 --end 2009/11/01
09-Aug-01 Budget transaction    Cash:NewCar                    $200         $200
09-Sep-01 Budget transaction    Cash:NewCar                    $200         $400
09-Oct-01 Budget transaction    Cash:NewCar                    $200         $600
end test
